---
const steps = [
  { cmd: 'Get 3+ Linux servers', detail: 'Bare metal, VMs, or cloud instances' },
  { cmd: 'Install Kubernetes', detail: 'kubeadm, k3s, or Cluster API' },
  { cmd: 'Deploy networking', detail: 'Kube-OVN for CNI + tenant isolation' },
  { cmd: 'Install kcp', detail: 'Multi-tenant control plane' },
  { cmd: 'Deploy Cloud Operator', detail: 'Connects kcp to infrastructure' },
  { cmd: 'Log in and use the cloud', detail: 'Your own multi-tenant platform, ready to go' },
];
---

<section id="getting-started" class="relative py-28 md:py-36">
  <div class="divider-glow absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="reveal text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-400 tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Quick Start</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-5 tracking-tight">
        Zero to Cloud
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 font-light">
        From bare servers to a working multi-tenant cloud platform.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps timeline -->
    <div class="reveal relative max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">
      <!-- Vertical line -->
      <div class="absolute left-[23px] top-2 bottom-2 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500/30 via-cyan-500/20 to-indigo-500/30 hidden md:block"></div>

      <div class="space-y-1 stagger-children">
        {steps.map(({ cmd, detail }, i) => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5 group py-3">
            <div class="relative flex-shrink-0 z-10">
              <div class="w-[46px] h-[46px] rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] group-hover:border-white/[0.15] group-hover:bg-white/[0.06] flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2">
              <p class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-0.5">{cmd}</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">{detail}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Terminal -->
    <div class="reveal max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
      <div class="border-gradient rounded-2xl glow-cyan">
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3.5 border-b border-white/5">
            <div class="flex gap-1.5">
              <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-white/10"></span>
              <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-white/10"></span>
              <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-white/10"></span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[11px] text-slate-600 font-mono ml-2">What tenants see</span>
          </div>
          <pre class="p-5 text-sm overflow-x-auto font-['JetBrains_Mono',monospace] leading-relaxed"><code class="text-slate-400"><span class="text-blue-400">$</span> kubectl get virtualmachines
<span class="text-slate-600">NAME      CORES   MEMORY   STATUS    AGE</span>
<span class="text-slate-300">dev-box   4       16Gi     <span class="text-emerald-400">Running</span>   3m</span>
<span class="text-slate-300">ml-gpu    8       64Gi     <span class="text-emerald-400">Running</span>   12m</span>

<span class="text-blue-400">$</span> kubectl get notebooks
<span class="text-slate-600">NAME       GPU    STATUS    URL                                   AGE</span>
<span class="text-slate-300">ml-work    A100   <span class="text-emerald-400">Running</span>   https://nb.cloud.example.com          5m</span></code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-xs text-slate-600 mt-4">No pods. No nodes. No clusters. Just your resources.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal text-center">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/faroshq/neocloud/blob/main/demo.md"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 hover:from-blue-500 hover:to-cyan-500 transition-all hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20"
      >
        Read the Full Guide
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
